# ngx_http_heavybag_module - Referer header signature blocklist
#
# Format: one PCRE2 pattern per line, optional trailing action token.
#   <pattern>[ <action>]      action in { 404 (default), 403, 444 }
#
# Patterns are matched case-insensitively against the %-decoded Referer
# request header. Known referrer-spoof / scanner markers are the target.
# Patterns sharing an action compile into one alternation; hot-reloadable.

# ---- known hostile / spoofed referrers -------------------------------------
evil\.example         404
semalt\.com           403

# ---- injection in the referer ----------------------------------------------
<script               444
